headline: BAE Systems Wins $473M Deal to Produce 40 M109A7 Paladin Howitzer
summary: BAESY secures a $473M contract to build 40 M109A7 Paladin howitzer sets, strengthening the U.S. Army's firepower and its armored vehicle footprint.
